_sText:
First of all the map prefix "de_" means that this custom-map is featuring 
one or more bombzones(in this particular case it's two). The setting
features a large storage building, a subway station, a useable gate, a
tunnel and a minor house block. The Terrorist spawn is right outside the 
storage building. The Counter-Terrorist spawn is inside the subway station.
To locate and finde the bombzones, please use the ingame radar.
